### --- Flow: create, patch isDone, verify ---

### 1) Create a new todo to update later
POST http://localhost:8085/api/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Task to patch isDone",
  "priority": "medium",
  "isDone": false
}

### 2) Fetch all todos to locate the new task's id (field: id)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/todo

### 3) Replace <PUT_ID_HERE> with the id from step 2 and patch isDone=true
PATCH http://localhost:8085/api/todo/68d6bb7cfead541a8a670029
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDone": false
}

### 4) Verify the record is updated (isDone should be true for that id)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/todo